          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How much does a bookkeeping cleanup cost?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Cleanup costs start at $2,500 for 1-3 months of records. The price scales with the volume of work and complexity, but most clients see significant ROI through recovered deductions and avoided penalties.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How long does a cleanup take?</h3>
